OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,FIt is supposed to be a projection of
OL,7,FMoscow's military strength, but
OL,8,FSaturday's Victory Day parade in Red
OL,9,FSquare only revealed Russia's weakness
OL,10,F` ITV News Bulletin Reporter Philip
OL,11,FSime has more
OL,13,FRussia's president Vladimir Putin said
OL,14,Fhe is confident of victory in Ukraine
OL,15,Fduring a scaled-back annual military
OL,16,Fparade in Moscow as a three-day
OL,17,Fceasefire took effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
