PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778454187
OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,FPutin was able to make his claim in
OL,7,Frelative safety, after Ukraine
OL,8,Fpromised not to attack the Victory Day
OL,9,Fparade in the Russian capital on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FHis comments suggest there is little
OL,13,Fhope in extending the temporary
OL,14,Fceasefire, which is expected to run
OL,15,Ffrom Saturday through Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
