PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778454187
OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,FFor the first time in nearly two
OL,7,Fdecades, the parade on Red Square,
OL,8,Fcommemorating the defeat of Nazi
OL,9,FGermany in the Second World War, did
OL,10,Fnot include tanks, missiles and other
OL,11,Fheavy equipment, aside from a
OL,12,Ftraditional flyover of combat jets.
OL,14,FSecurity was tight in Moscow as Putin
OL,15,Fand several foreign leaders attended
OL,16,Fthe parade, following concerns about
OL,17,Fpossible Ukrainian attempts to disrupt
OL,18,Fthe festivities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
