CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778454187
OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,F"Victory has always been and will be
OL,7,Fours," Putin said. "The key to success
OL,8,Fis our moral strength, courage and
OL,9,Fvalour, our unity and ability to
OL,10,Fendure anything and overcome any
OL,11,Fchallenge."
OL,13,FOfficials explained the sudden change
OL,14,Fof format by the "current operational
OL,15,Fsituation" and said that additional
OL,16,Fsecurity measures have been taken in
OL,17,Fresponse to the threat of Ukrainian
OL,18,Fattacks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@FO]oD@TOUsD@KO]vD@ROUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
