OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778454187
OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,FNeither of those earlier ceasefires
OL,7,Fheld, however, as each party traded
OL,8,Fblame for continuing attacks.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FUS President Donald Trump announced on
OL,16,FFriday that Russia and Ukraine had
OL,17,Fbowed to his request for a ceasefire
OL,18,Frunning Saturday through Monday and an
OL,19,Fexchange of prisoners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
