FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778454187
OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,FHe declared that the break in fighting
OL,7,Fcould be the "beginning of the end" of
OL,8,Fthe war, although Putin's rhetoric
OL,9,Fcasts doubt on this claim.
OL,11,FZelenskyy, who said earlier this week
OL,12,Fthat the Russian authorities "fear
OL,13,Fdrones may buzz over Red Square" on
OL,14,FMay 9, followed up on Trump's
OL,15,Fstatement by issuing a decree
OL,16,Fmockingly permitting Russia to hold
OL,17,Fits Victory Day celebrations,
OL,18,Fdeclaring Red Square temporarily off-
OL,19,Flimits for Ukrainian strikes.
