OL,3,CRussia holds scaled down Victory Day
OL,4,Cparade amid three-day ceasefire
OL,6,FKremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov
OL,7,Fshrugged off Zelenskyy's decree as a
OL,8,F"silly joke." "We don't need anyone's
OL,9,Fpermission to be proud of our Victory
OL,10,FDay," Peskov told reporters.
